snippet.title: Amber Heard ADMITS Her Baby Announcement Is A Publicity Stunt...
snippet.description:
Amber Heard ADMITS Her Baby Announcement Is A Publicity Stunt...
To say that the case between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard is one of the most interesting cases thus far would be an understatement. It just so happens to be that as the days get closer to their court date that the news that gets brought to light happens to be more and more shocking. In more recent news, it was shared that Amber Heard had a baby, and no we are not saying that she was hiding her pregnancy all this time, but regardless of how it happened, Amber Heard has a baby girl. Now there are not many good things that people on social media have to say about this news and it seems that Amber Heard has come forward to address some questions in regard to the matter. Allow us to break all the recent news down for you but first be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel below.
